{"tid":2329074,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"大學生入嚟，我教你點樣用維基百科去搵references","createTime":"2020-12-17T03:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T15:55:16.000Z","uid":71237,"like":301,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"ad0f8a1a453ad368972142ac78b18094ca63cc71","tid":2329074,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T03:47:56.000Z","msg":"次次講親維基百科，都會有一堆人懶醒咁話「維基百科人人都可以改，根本唔可靠」「讀過大學都知道維基百科唔可以做references」。<br />\n<br />\n無錯，有正常智力嘅大學生都知道唔可以直接引用維基百科做references，但唔代表你寫論文嗰陣維基百科幫唔到手。我今日就教大家點樣用維基百科。<br />\n<br />\n例如我想寫一篇關於「存在主義」的論文。去到維基百科，你會見到內文會有[1][2]依啲數字。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7gHFFmL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7gHFFmL.jpg&h=a00d52be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多人唔知道<strong><span class=\"x-large\">寫維基百科都要落references</span></strong>。你追蹤返依啲數字，就已經可以搵到一大堆書籍、論文俾你做references。傻嘅先會直接引用維基百科，識玩嘅應該睇返啲人寫維基百科嗰陣落咗咩references。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QFPAuf1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQFPAuf1.jpg&h=af11a977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連新世紀福音戰士(EVA)都有630個references，而且啲references唔係普通討論區、2ch，而係新聞報導、書籍、學術論文等等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tCD9yJ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtCD9yJ1.jpg&h=cefff8dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後講多次重點 ：<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">寫維基百科都要落references</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">寫維基百科都要落references</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">寫維基百科都要落references</span></strong>"},{"pid":"0744251366c06ef2cf4273894f32215d828b39a8","tid":2329074,"uid":316130,"like":397,"dislike":0,"score":397,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T03:49:39.000Z","msg":"正常大學生都咁做過啦，話唔睇維基真係唔睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5547f3f2bf5d4855bae36e810ddae9cefd8abdf","tid":2329074,"uid":53798,"like":11,"dislike":46,"score":-35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T03:50:18.0